545
00:42:50,800 --> 00:42:54,910
To nie je dobrý škriatok, ale netvor.

546
00:42:54,910 --> 00:42:59,270
Máš pravdu. Je to netvor. Blbec.

547
00:42:59,270 --> 00:43:00,790
Hej.

