559
00:44:21,480 --> 00:44:24,530
Nechoď. Poď so mnou.

560
00:44:28,380 --> 00:44:31,240
V žiadnom prípade. Prečo by som mala?

561
00:44:31,240 --> 00:44:32,770
Koľko mi môžeš zaplatiť?

562
00:44:32,770 --> 00:44:36,310
Aj keď mi dáš 500 Wonov,
nepôjdem s tebou.

563
00:44:36,310 --> 00:44:39,180
